      "html": "<section class=\"slide titleAndSubtitle\"><h1 id=\"imp8c9dad1\" class=\" hidden taleem-heading-lg \" > Expanding (a+b)^2 </h1><h2 id=\"imp8c9dad2\" class=\" hidden taleem-heading-md \" > Testing EQ slide pacing and reasoning flow </h2></section>",
